NOTE ON GAME ASSETS: This engine and toolkit are MIT-licensed. The bundled
example regions (examples/) use procedurally generated art and no Nintendo or
Game Freak assets. Pokémon species names, move names, and other game data
(derived from the PokeAPI database, itself CC-BY-NC) are used for engine
compatibility purposes only. Do not redistribute Nintendo-owned sprite artwork
(e.g. downloaded via `pkmn-fetch-data --sprites`) in any game folder you
share publicly.
